{"tid":1776814,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【獻計】和理非已經山窮水盡，運動注定俾港共睇死","createTime":"2019-12-09T19:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T03:06:10.000Z","uid":238040,"like":16,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d468ddc0bdfe4abf8a73e059f3fb17c9bde7d88d","tid":1776814,"uid":238040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T19:37:35.000Z","msg":"越來越灰心，無野可以做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">手足上庭遭警暴，聲淚俱下和理割。黑警講錯當笑話，勇武屠龍氣盡失。</span><br />\n昨日新疆，今日香港。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n103萬,200萬,80萬<br />\n8月5日多區開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n痴撚左線既兩星期黎明行動<br />\n之後黃店為左支持香港，<span style=\"color: gold;\">自己都要濫炒埋而放棄生意支持三罷。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非呢？勇武被人大搜捕清算後係咪無野可以做到？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">定係天真爛漫地捐錢星火，遊行捐濕尻機構去買贖罪卷</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">和理非要正式升級<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n三罷就係和理非最強武器，點解時間越後越淡忘？</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DRXTRkM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDRXTRkM.jpg&h=4722526c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J0RQTy5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ0RQTy5.jpg&h=89ebbc4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MRojMT3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMRojMT3.jpg&h=6d2e4479&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nbzKX0H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnbzKX0H.jpg&h=39c9296c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vXaeANm.jp